title.narrative: GUATEMALA Maternal and Infant Health and Nutrition

description.narrative: The proposed Project aims to support the Government of Guatemala to: (a) improve maternal and infant health in the project's 40 areas of intervention; and (b) reduce chronic malnutrition among children younger than 2 years of age in the rural areas of the 70 municipalities targeted by the project.
